3. Missing Requirement
🔴 This will be evaluated once correct test_results.csv file is submitted.

💡 Suggestions

Add a brief “How we calculated this” snippet to quotes that lists inputs and rules used (e.g., base price × qty, bulk discount tier, shipping method, taxes). Keep it to 2–4 bullet points for readability.
Standardize a short reason code in responses (e.g., OUT_OF_STOCK, QTY_LIMIT_EXCEEDED, DELIVERY_WINDOW_UNAVAILABLE) paired with a human readable explanation. This keeps outputs both explainable and consistent.
Ensure PII minimization: only reflect what’s necessary to complete/confirm the transaction (mask emails and phone numbers, avoid storing or re-printing unneeded identifiers).
Maintain a customer-safe error layer: convert any stack traces or raw DB errors into plain-language messages with next steps (“Please try a smaller quantity or choose a different paper type.”).
